sentence.text: We chose to study protein transport-branching involved in blood vessel morphogenesis rather than wild muscle organ development branching involved in blood vessel morphogenesis because unlike full length sema3E, the major p61-Sema3E peptide that is produced by cleavage of sema3E with furin like pro-protein convertases activates signal transduction mediated by the ErbB2 receptor and can promote tumor metastasis in addition to its anti-angiogenic activity.
